properties.Name: ChannelProductCooperativePayment
properties.Description:
Payments made to a channel in support of products sold by or distributed by the channel.

These funds are to cultivate, expand and support channel product capabilities etc.

Columns.Name: ChannelId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Channel.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the associated cooperative payment is due the Channel.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the associated cooperative payment is due the Channel.

Columns.Name: ChannelCoopPaymentsAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of channel coop payments made to the channel.
